  "body": "1. Audio message icon z-index should be increased, keyboard should not overlap it.\r\n\r\n<img width=\"250px\" src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/22799766/b38e987d-524c-4947-835c-49048fc57dda\"/>\r\n\r\n\r\n2. send button should be same size as record button - currently record looks slightly bigger.\r\n\r\n3. send audio button should be adjusted, not aligned (verify)\r\n\r\n4. There is also an issue where Audio message animation can be slow.\r\nwhen the user types and sends a message too fast and sometimes the slow animation of changing the audio button > the send button causes the audio to start recording instead of sending the message.\r\n\r\nIssue 3 and Issue 4 are related and cause the behavior in the video below.\r\nIf you hit the area where the `send` button does not overlap the `audio` button, while the change animation is in progress, audio recording starts instead of sending a message.\r\n\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/67952253/07dafa91-bac0-4fed-ab64-d5414eecdca0\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nDesigns:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/wA8Epdki2OWa8Vr067PCNQ/Composer-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=2102-171075&t=zc32OqUZuDYsU1VJ-0\r\n",
